oice, Wait, Parallel, Map, Succeed/Fail\n• Task state — usually invokes Lambda / ECS / HTTP\n• Transitions — AWS stores progress and retries\n• Execution history — managed run log on AWS side\n\nYou define the graph; AWS runs and persists it.","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Core concepts:\n• State machine — your workflow definition (ASL JSON)\n• States — Task, Choice, Wait, Parallel, Map, Succeed/Fail\n• Task state — usually invokes Lambda / ECS / HTTP\n• Transitions — AWS stores progress and retries\n• Execution history — managed run log on AWS side\n\nYou define the graph; AWS runs and persists it.","autoResize":false,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":340,"index":"c1Hi"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["EHwCuGlNlISgh2UALe0Wr"],"frameId":null,"seed":1823012166,"versionNonce":1922388122,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784789802835,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"ellipse","id":"acV1b9oR-_ZQGTO-EUPsn","x":-13501.504583366745,"y":28893.760705357716,"width":40,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#22C55E","backgroundColor":"#22C55E","roundness":null,"version":340,"index":"c1Hj"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["EHwCuGlNlISgh2UALe0Wr"],"frameId":null,"seed":799431814,"versionNonce":681123334,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784789802835,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"text","id":"D5kjl2tidwv7j86vubLXS","x":-13490.504583366745,"y":28903.760705357716,"width":160,"height":20,"strokeColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"text":"I","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"I","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":340,"index":"c1Hk"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"group