 step\n• Worker — orchestrates: load run, pick executor, checkpoint, enqueue next\n• Executors — API / Conditional / Function / Integration / Response\n• Durable Lambda (or similar sandbox) — ONLY for untrusted Function code isolation\n• Postgres — workflow_runs, current_node_id, error, context\n\nFlow:\nenqueue execute(node) → success → checkpoint → enqueue successor(s)\nfailure → store error → resume later from that node","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Core concepts:\n• Queue — job per node step\n• Worker — orchestrates: load run, pick executor, checkpoint, enqueue next\n• Executors — API / Conditional / Function / Integration / Response\n• Durable Lambda (or similar sandbox) — ONLY for untrusted Function code isolation\n• Postgres — workflow_runs, current_node_id, error, context\n\nFlow:\nenqueue execute(node) → success → checkpoint → enqueue successor(s)\nfailure → store error → resume later from that node","autoResize":false,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":342,"index":"c1IQ"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["ON1p5qi_mOY_UM2q6fmPd"],"frameId":null,"seed":718103622,"versionNonce":24125722,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784789802835,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"ellipse","id":"azMesWQ5lBN7vrkAE_-nP","x":-13501.504583366745,"y":30545.760705357716,"width":40,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#22C55E","backgroundColor":"#22C55E","roundness":null,"version":340,"index":"c1IR"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["ON1p5qi_mOY_UM2q6fmPd"],"frameId":null,"seed":761588614,"versionNonce":636589446,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784789802835,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"text","id":"Mv3rJATDYDp4E1svOjwqL","x":-13490.504583366745,"y":30555.760705357716,"width":160,"height":20,"strokeColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundColor":"trans