  Allowed from              →  To           Idempotent?\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/pause                    pending, running        →  paused       200 if already paused\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/resume                   paused                  →  running      200 if already running\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/stop                     pending, running, paused → cancelled   200 if already cancelled\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/retry                    failed                  →  running      200 if already running\n\nWorker transitions (automatic)\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\npending  →  running          worker picks up job\nrunning  →  completed       all nodes succeed\nrunning  →  failed           node error (error jsonb set)\n\nInvalid → 409 Conflict     e.g. Retry on paused · Stop on completed · Pause on failed","originalText":"API transitions                          Allowed from              →  To           Idempotent?\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/pause                    pending, running        →  paused       200 if already paused\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/resume                   paused                  →  running      200 if already running\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/stop                     pending, running, paused → cancelled   200 if already cancelled\nPOST /v1/runs/:id/retry                    failed                  →  running      200 if already running\n\nWorker transitions (automatic)\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\npending  →  running          worker picks up job\nrunning  →  completed       all nodes succeed\nrunning  →  failed           node error (error jsonb set)\n\nInvalid → 409 Conflict     e.g. Retry on paused · Stop on completed · Pause on failed","fontSize":12,"fontFa